snippet.textDisplay: What Ryan and the judges did for this young man was outstanding. Everyone needs to have their moment in life, and this dream that Doug Kiker  was able to live out because of the love and compassion you showed, will be something he and his beautiful family will cherish and remember for a lifetime. This show was so heartwarming, and I applaud all of you for the care and compassion you show the contestants, AND was most happy to see Lionel put one of the contestants in his place, he certainly needed to be humbled! GREAT SHOW!!! I can hardly wait to see what's next :)
